			"condition": "routineName=='BasicWarrior' && !alreadyPlayed",
			"prompt": "Basic Warrior. <break size='0.3'/>Now let's get ready. You'll want to make sure there's plenty of space around you, for moving around. If you want, you can unplug me and take me to a better spot. <break size='0.5'/> When you're ready to start, say I'm ready!",
